      • copyBytes

        public static void copyBytes(java.io.InputStream in,
                             java.io.OutputStream out,
                             int buffSize,
                             boolean close)
                      throws java.io.IOException
        Copies from one stream to another.
        参数:
        in - InputStream to read from
        out - OutputStream to write to
        buffSize - the size of the buffer
        close - whether or not close the InputStream and OutputStream at the end. The streams are closed in the finally clause.
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - thrown if an error occurred while writing to the output stream

      • copyBytes

        public static void copyBytes(java.io.InputStream in,
                             java.io.OutputStream out)
                      throws java.io.IOException
        Copies from one stream to another. closes the input and output streams at the end.
        参数:
        in - InputStream to read from
        out - OutputStream to write to
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - thrown if an I/O error occurs while copying

      • copyBytes

      • readFully

        public static void readFully(java.io.InputStream in,
                             byte[] buf,
                             int off,
                             int len)
                      throws java.io.IOException
        Reads len bytes in a loop.
        参数:
        in - The InputStream to read from
        buf - The buffer to fill
        off - offset from the buffer
        len - the length of bytes to read
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - if it could not read requested number of bytes for any reason (including EOF)

      • skipFully

        public static void skipFully(java.io.InputStream in,
                             long len)
                      throws java.io.IOException
        Similar to readFully(). Skips bytes in a loop.
        参数:
        in - The InputStream to skip bytes from
        len - number of bytes to skip
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - if it could not skip requested number of bytes for any reason (including EOF)

      • cleanup

        public static void cleanup(org.slf4j.Logger log,
                           java.lang.AutoCloseable... closeables)
        Close the AutoCloseable objects and ignore any Exception or null pointers. Must only be used for cleanup in exception handlers.
        参数:
        log - the log to record problems to at debug level. Can be null.
        closeables - the objects to close

      • closeStream

        public static void closeStream(java.io.Closeable stream)
        Closes the stream ignoring IOException. Must only be called in cleaning up from exception handlers.
        参数:
        stream - the stream to close

      • closeSocket

        public static void closeSocket(java.net.Socket sock)
        Closes the socket ignoring IOException.
        参数:
        sock - the socket to close

      • closeAll

        public static void closeAll(java.lang.Iterable<? extends java.lang.AutoCloseable> closeables)
                     throws java.lang.Exception
        Closes all AutoCloseable objects in the parameter, suppressing exceptions. Exception will be emitted after calling close() on every object.
        参数:
        closeables - iterable with closeables to close.
        抛出:
        java.lang.Exception - collected exceptions that occurred during closing

      • closeAllQuietly

        public static void closeAllQuietly(java.lang.Iterable<? extends java.lang.AutoCloseable> closeables)
        Closes all elements in the iterable with closeQuietly().

      • closeQuietly

        public static void closeQuietly(java.lang.AutoCloseable closeable)

        Important: This method is expected to never throw an exception.
